item.title: Io Games Wormate
item.description: “Wormate io” is another multiplayer online game based on the classic “Snake”. You can play it absolutely free, enjoying high-quality and very funny animation. Unlike the obsolete counterpart, in the process of passing you will have to eat not boring points, but mouth-watering sweets - cakes, cakes, sweets, etc. And the character himself compares favorably with the minimalist predecessor. Outwardly, the snake resembles the hero of an animated film - a perky physiognomy, mischievous eyes, cheerful colors.
